# connect in postfix server mail local
telnet 0 25

# connect in postfix server remote
telnet ol9-server01 25


# send mail examples

# simple test
HELO lpic2.com.br
MAIL FROM: silvestrini
RCPT TO: vagrant
DATA
Message for test postfix by Silvestrini
Learning about postfix mail server
.

# teste aliases

